                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10009" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-1136</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">228 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数智化转型与服务化融合创新：艾普达智慧运维的协同生态构建</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital and Intelligent Transformation with Service Integration Innovation: Collaborative Ecosystem Construction for Aipuda’s Smart Operations and Maintenance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朱煜明，赵嘉雯，肖平，赵伟，刘敏</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">艾普达技术服务有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数智化转型；组织重塑；服务革新；协同生态构建</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">digital and intelligent transformation, organizational restructuring, service innovation, collaborative ecosystem construction</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作为电力运维领域的领军企业，艾普达技术服务有限公司（以下简称“艾普达”），因2019年某变电站蓄电池故障引发的重大停电事故，深刻认识到传统人工巡检模式的低效与滞后，于2018年启动数智化转型。
在数智化转型层面，艾普达依托物联网、大数据与AI技术，自主研发BEM（蓄电池均衡管理）系统，通过部署传感器实时采集电池电压、电流、内阻等关键参数，结合机器学习算法构建“感知-分析-决策”一体化智慧运维平台；在组织重塑层面，艾普达采取 “保留 + 创新” 策略，留存部分传统运维团队服务保守型客户，同时成立智慧科技事业部整合跨领域人才，化解组织变革阻力。在服务革新层面，艾普达基于数据驱动实现三重革新：引入了电池远程核容系统，实现运维模式从被动到主动的变革、精准测算蓄电池 SOC/SOH ，实现决策依据从经验到数据的转变、针对不同客户提供定制化方案，完成服务从标准化到差异化的转型。在生态构建层面，艾普达以 BEM 系统为枢纽，联动产业链上下游，与互联网企业及科研院校合作，打通信息孤岛，拓展系统在电力、通信等多领域的应用。
转型后成效显著：经济效益方面，电池投资与维护成本分别降低20%和30%；社会效益层面，故障预警减少停电事故，智能充放电技术降低能耗与污染；技术优势层面，其单体均衡算法与远程核容技术处于行业领先地位，为电力运维数智化提供实践范式。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a leading enterprise in the power operation and maintenance (O&amp;M) sector, Aipuda Technology Service Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;Aipuda&quot;) profoundly recognized the inefficiency and lag of the traditional manual inspection model due to a major power outage caused by battery failures at a substation in 2019, and thus launched its digital and intelligent transformation in 2018.
In terms of digital and intelligent transformation, relying on the Internet of Things (IoT), big data, and AI technologies, Aipuda independently developed the BEM (Battery Balance Management) system. It deploys sensors to collect key parameters of batteries in real time, such as voltage, current, and internal resistance, and combines machine learning algorithms to build an integrated &quot;perception-analysis-decision-making&quot; smart O&amp;M platform. At the organizational restructuring level, Aipuda adopted a &quot;retention + innovation&quot; strategy: it retained part of the traditional O&amp;M team to serve conservative customers, while establishing a Smart Technology Division to integrate cross-disciplinary talents and resolve resistance to organizational changes. In the aspect of service innovation, Aipuda achieved three major innovations driven by data: it introduced a remote battery capacity verification system to transform the O&amp;M model from passive response to active prevention; it accurately calculated the battery&#39;s SOC (State of Charge) and SOH (State of Health) to shift the decision-making basis from experience to data; and it provided customized solutions for different customers to upgrade services from standardization to differentiation. At the ecosystem construction level, with the BEM system as the core hub, Aipuda connected the upstream and downstream of the industrial chain, collaborated with Internet enterprises and scientific research institutions, broke down information silos, and expanded the application of the system in multiple fields such as electric power and communications.
The transformation has yielded remarkable results: in terms of economic benefits, battery investment and maintenance costs have been reduced by 20% and 30% respectively; in terms of social benefits, fault early warning has reduced power outages, and intelligent charging and discharging technology has lowered energy consumption and pollution; in terms of technical advantages, its cell balancing algorithm and remote capacity verification technology lead the industry, providing a practical model for the digital and intelligent transformation of power O&amp;M.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》、《服务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数智化转型的内涵和驱动因素；服务创新四维度模型理论；商业生态系统理论；企业可持续商业战略理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-10</td>
                            </tr>
